Breadcrumbs
===========

Really simple breadcrumbs for your rails app.


Example
=======

In your controller or view:
  
  add_breadcrumb "My site", '/' # Linked breadcrumb
  add_breadcrumb "Edit"         # Breadcrumb without link

In your view:

  <%= breadcrumbs %>


